room_title: Escape room "Nature Ninja" by Escape Woods in Atlanta
room_address: 628 Sleepy Hollow Rd Powder Springs, GA 30127
room_description: Nature Ninja is designed for kids between the ages of 6-9 and blends fun physical activities with nature based STEM education. In this adventure your kids will need to complete a series of obstacles set in a 200 year old hardwood forest while learning about native Georgia animals and plants.
